## 🧠 Technologies Used

- Python • Transformers • Hugging Face • Conda • Jupyter • Git LFS  
- Datasets: Alpaca, CNN/DailyMail, Evol-Codealpaca  
- LLM: Meta LLaMA 2 – 7B Chat HF  
- Tools: Intel Extension for Transformers

---

## 📌 Objective

This project proves the feasibility of running and fine-tuning powerful LLMs on standard CPU setups, enabling local deployment of intelligent chatbots without the need for expensive GPU infrastructure.

